Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,《法外情真》前情回顾\N{\fs12}Previously on The Guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我快要死了\N{\fs12}I'm dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么  - 肌萎缩性侧索硬化症\N{\fs12}- What? - ALS.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,卢伽雷氏症\N{\fs12}Lou Gehrig's disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想律所的事情\N{\fs12}I been thinking about the firm,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候让你接手管理合伙人了\N{\fs12}It's time for you to be managing partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我一直都\N{\fs12}I, I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,试着平等对待每一个人\N{\fs12}Try to treat everybody the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你试了  但没成功\N{\fs12}You may try, but you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的那些关于尼古拉斯的话\N{\fs12}What you said about Nicolas...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你是对的\N{\fs12}I think you were right,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有的时候\N{\fs12}there are times...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是会偏心他  只想让你知道  呃\N{\fs12}I favor him, just want you to know that, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我记住了\N{\fs12}I'm gonna keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗\N{\fs12}ls something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我用斯坦霍普的交易为例\N{\fs12}I used the Stanhope deal as precedent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那是股票交易  这是资产出售\N{\fs12}Well, that's a stock deal. This is an asset sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么时候的事\N{\fs12}When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,巴特勒现在正在出售资产  这就是作为资产出售交易的原因\N{\fs12}Butler's now selling its assets. That's what makes it an asset sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  它最开始是股票交易  不是吗\N{\fs12}Well, it was originally a stock deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对  但现在它是资产出售了\N{\fs12}That's right, but now it's an asset sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我会修改的  马上就改\N{\fs12}Well, I'll revise it. I'll do it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:00:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸今天结束前就要一份起草协议\N{\fs12}My father's gonna need a draft of this by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不告诉我发生了什么  我就不能起草协议\N{\fs12}I can't draft an agreement if you don't tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没人可以\N{\fs12}No one can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  如果我没有被请去参加会议或者电话会议什么的\N{\fs12}I mean, if I'm not invited to the meetings or sitting in on the conference calls...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我花了2100个小时\N{\fs12}I billed 2, 100 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,带了40万的生意进来\N{\fs12}brought in $400,000 in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那  那非常好\N{\fs12}That's--that's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以让我来起草协议\N{\fs12}So let me revise the agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我知道了这是资产出售\N{\fs12}now that I know it's an asset sale,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们可以假装什么问题都没发生过  好吗\N{\fs12}and we can pretend there was never a problem, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我会处理的\N{\fs12}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.36,0:01:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了  我是认真的\N{\fs12}I've had enough. I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好  你看  只要坚持到明天  好吗\N{\fs12}Yeah. Look, just hang in there until tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:01:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我来晚了\N{\fs12}Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs12}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这个女人  她快把我弄疯了\N{\fs12}This woman at work, she's just driving me nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我给了她最简单的工作\N{\fs12}I give her the simplest assignments,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样  她搞砸了然后还怪我\N{\fs12}and no matter what, she screws it up and then she blames me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs12}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不  没关系\N{\fs12}No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这个孩子的事  不管是男孩还是女孩\N{\fs12}About this baby thing, whether it's a boy or girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望到时候再知晓\N{\fs12}I prefer to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  这确实会让人感觉很惊喜\N{\fs12}You know, it's just something about it being a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉像作弊了一样\N{\fs12}Plus it feels like cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好像在圣诞前夜打开了一个礼物\N{\fs12}It's like opening a present on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  好  行  我是说  如果你不想知道的话\N{\fs12}All right. Okay. All right. I mean, if you don't want to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不能相信你和苏珊娜·佩尔睡过\N{\fs12}I just can't believe that you slept with Suzanne Pell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不一直看到她  你知道吗  我还要和她一起工作\N{\fs12}I have to see her all the time, you know? I have to work with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我怀着你的孩子  你睡着她\N{\fs12}And I'm pregnant with your baby, and you sleep with her
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候  我就是\N{\fs12}and sometimes I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  我还是不敢相信\N{\fs12}I don't know. I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  儿子  - 爸\N{\fs12}- Hey, son. - Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗\N{\fs12}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还好  呃\N{\fs12}Good. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 都好了吗  - 对\N{\fs12}- All set? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  尼克\N{\fs12}Hey, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,桑德拉\N{\fs12}Sandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就好了\N{\fs12}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我自己走\N{\fs12}Yep. On my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我送你出去  好吗  - 好\N{\fs12}- I'll walk you out, okay? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,马上回来\N{\fs12}Be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,过得挺愉快的\N{\fs12}Well, that was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯  谢谢  - 很高兴你能过来\N{\fs12}- Yeah. Thanks. - Glad you could come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想和你谈谈关于桑德拉的事\N{\fs12}Been meaning to talk to you about Sandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她和我在过去几周一直在一起\N{\fs12}She and I've been spending a little time together the last few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs12}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这表示我们都很享受在一起的时光\N{\fs12}Well, it means we enjoy spending time with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你们是朋友吗\N{\fs12}So you're friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们享受彼此的陪伴\N{\fs12}We enjoy each other's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个好姑娘\N{\fs12}She's a great gal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,和孩子们相处的也好\N{\fs12}Real good with children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她有个女儿  10岁大\N{\fs12}She has a little girl, ten years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她和香农相处得很好  所以\N{\fs12}She gets along great with Shannon, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这段关系的时间点似乎还挺巧的  你不觉得吗\N{\fs12}The timing of this relationship seems a little convenient, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  你不用担心那个\N{\fs12}No. No. You don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:05:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  我没计划支持她成为合伙人\N{\fs12}See, I wasn't planning on supporting her for partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fs12}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这样  你和她在一起的事\N{\fs12}And with this, you being involved with her
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不能再说不了  理由很明显\N{\fs12}makes it very dimicult for me to say no, for obvious reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你得做你认为对的事  儿子\N{\fs12}You have to do what you think is right, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,资产购买协议  抱歉  交晚了\N{\fs12}Asset purchase agreement. Sorry it's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,第一稿有些问题\N{\fs12}There were some complications with the first draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我会看的  然后明早去和巴特勒谈\N{\fs12}Okay, I'll look it over, and I'll talk to Butler in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 早上好  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Good morning. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要公司的海盗队的票吗\N{\fs12}You want the firm's Pirate tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我有海盗队比赛的票\N{\fs12}I have tickets to the Pirates' game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  谢谢\N{\fs12}No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 祝一天愉快  - 你也是\N{\fs12}- Have a nice day. - You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  你好吗  怎么样了\N{\fs12}Hey. How are you-- How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事  - 好  好\N{\fs12}- Fine. - Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呃  我  - 对  一会见\N{\fs12}-- Well, I... - Yeah. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我知道这事不用多说  但是  呃\N{\fs12}Listen, I know it goes without saying, but, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不跟别人提桑德拉的事我会很感激的  好吗\N{\fs12}I'd appreciate if you don't mention this Sandra thing to anybody, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,当然卡尔德只给了我们两周时间\N{\fs12}Of course Kalder's only giving us two weeks to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他为什么会提供那么高昂的溢价\N{\fs12}But that's why he's offering such a large premium.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但是就像我说的  查理说了不\N{\fs12}But like I said, Charlie said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他还是做了什么  我是说  他只是不停地摇头\N{\fs12}I think he did anyway. I mean, he just kept shaking his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他都不能理解我说的话事情会很困难\N{\fs12}It's hard to know if he even understood what I was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他病的太严重了\N{\fs12}He's so sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事的进展会非常快\N{\fs12}The MS has progressed very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以等到查理同意了\N{\fs12}We could wait until Charlie passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们会错过溢价\N{\fs12}We'll lose the premium.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是我想说的\N{\fs12}I was gonna say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么其他特殊的理由让查理不卖吗\N{\fs12}ls there any specific reason why Charlie won't sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  这就是事情奇怪的地方了\N{\fs12}No. That's why this is so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直在合适的时间说要卖掉\N{\fs12}He's always talked about selling, at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,努力工作  发展业务  套现\N{\fs12}Work hard, grow the business, cash out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我们可以用股东协议里的买卖条款\N{\fs12}Well, we can invoke the buy-sell clause in the stockholders agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,让你合理地买到查理股票\N{\fs12}Gives you the right to buy Charlie's stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那太浪费时间了\N{\fs12}It'd take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要做的是尽快安排一个和查理的律师\N{\fs12}What we need to do is to set up a meeting with Charlie's lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,见面的会议\N{\fs12}as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,像我说的  尼克  查理病得很严重\N{\fs12}Like I said, Nick. Charlie's very ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定那样做能帮上什么忙\N{\fs12}I'm not sure that's going to help very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  报价两周后就到期了  所以我们别无选择\N{\fs12}Well, the offer expires in two weeks, so we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你来做决定\N{\fs12}Your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我打赌离开西南部精神病院的感觉一定很不错\N{\fs12}I bet it feels good to be out of Southwestern.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你可不可以把耳机拿掉\N{\fs12}Maybe you could take the headphones off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就一分钟\N{\fs12}Just for a minute anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\fs12}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你在用一种  我很担心你的  表情在看我\N{\fs12}You're looking at me in that ''I'm so concerned'' kind of way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么  我试过上吊自杀\N{\fs12}Big deal. I tried to hang myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我知道\N{\fs12}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以别再像那样看着我了\N{\fs12}So stop looking at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,像哪样\N{\fs12}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好像我是疯子一样\N{\fs12}Like I'm crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有那样看你\N{\fs12}I'm not looking at you that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白你的感受\N{\fs12}The truth is I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白什么  - 想自杀\N{\fs12}- Get what? - Wanting to kill yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你做过吗\N{\fs12}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,做过  但那并不不表示\N{\fs12}I do, but that doesn't mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  我能和你谈谈吗\N{\fs12}Alvin. Can I talk to you for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,现在吗\N{\fs12}Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,马上回来  好吗\N{\fs12}Be right back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,德鲁·扬科夫斯基  他13岁\N{\fs12}Drew Jankowski. He's 13 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈死于一起车祸  没有爸爸\N{\fs12}Mother died in a car accident and there's no father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他想离开西南精神病院\N{\fs12}He's getting out of Southwestern Psychiatric Facility,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他需要找个地方待着\N{\fs12}and he needs a place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么他在西南精神病院  - 他试着自杀了两次\N{\fs12}- Why's he at Southwestern? - He tried to kill himself twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你反应过度了  露露\N{\fs12}You're over-reacting, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以处理这个孩子的安置听证会  看在上帝的份上\N{\fs12}I can handle the kid's placement hearing, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文  我只是想让尼克接手\N{\fs12}Alvin, I just want Nick to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔文最近  有点奇怪\N{\fs12}Alvin has been... kinda freaky lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  他一直在说来世怎么怎么样的\N{\fs12}I mean, he keeps talking about the next life and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我不觉得让他来处理这个孩子的事是个好主意\N{\fs12}So I don't think it's a good idea for him to work with this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好  听着  关于昨晚  我  呃\N{\fs12}Right. Listen, about last night, l, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想谈那个  好吗\N{\fs12}I don't want to talk about that, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,德鲁在会议室\N{\fs12}Drew's in the meeting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fs12}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没  我没事  谢谢\N{\fs12}Yeah, I'm okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃  只是被绊倒了\N{\fs12}l, uh, just tripped... over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事  就是被绊倒了  没什么\N{\fs12}I'm okay. I just tripped. No big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,第一件我们需要做的就是把你送去收容所\N{\fs12}First thing we need to do is to move you into a shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,然后找到和你一起生活的寄养家庭\N{\fs12}Then find you a foster family to live with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,最后就知道了上吊为什么没用\N{\fs12}Finally figured out why it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,套索上的线圈不够\N{\fs12}Not enough loops in the noose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,线圈可以让它保持住\N{\fs12}It's the loops that make it hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我很高兴线圈不够\N{\fs12}Well, I'm glad there weren't enough loops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能戴着它进法庭  你得把它拿下来\N{\fs12}You can't wear those in the courtroom. You have to take 'em off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,拿下来\N{\fs12}Take 'em off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很高兴你能来  尼克\N{\fs12}We appreciate where you're coming from, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是就像我告诉过你的  查理不想卖\N{\fs12}But like I told you, Charlie doesn't want to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他的公司\N{\fs12}And it is his company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,雷切尔在过去的四年里都是执行总裁\N{\fs12}RacheI's been the CEO for the past four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,查理拥有百分之七十六的股份\N{\fs12}Charlie owns 76% of the stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,格赛特先生有意识到这是格赛特纸业\N{\fs12}Does Mr. Gossett realize that this is the best offer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有史以来最好的报价吗\N{\fs12}that Gossett Paper will ever see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克是对的  亲爱的\N{\fs12}Nick's right, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个很好的机会  我真的觉得我们应该卖\N{\fs12}This is a great opportunity, and I really believe we should sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你\N{\fs12}Like I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚已经向查理解释过现状了\N{\fs12}I explained the situation to Charlie last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他传达给我的是  他不想卖\N{\fs12}He conveyed to me that he doesn't want to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他传达给你了吗\N{\fs12}He conveyed that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信他能明白你在对他说什么吗\N{\fs12}And you believe that he understood what you were conveying to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,查理能明白你今天在这里说的每一个字\N{\fs12}Charlie understands every single word you've said here today
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,和你说话时的语气\N{\fs12}and the tone with which it was said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,查理是个商人\N{\fs12}Charlie's a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他能明白我们说的话\N{\fs12}lf he understood what we were saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,回答 是  就能让他妻子的口袋里多出1500万美元\N{\fs12}that saying yes would put an extra $15 million in his wife's pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那么他就会同意这笔交易了\N{\fs12}he would agree to the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  先生  我想这次的会议可以结束了\N{\fs12}Thank you, gentlemen. I think this meeting is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那家伙完全恍惚了  - 我不这么想\N{\fs12}- The guy's completely out of it. - I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我看见他的眼睛来回地转  有几次他好像还点头了\N{\fs12}I mean, I saw his eyes moving back and forth, and he seemed to nod a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么样  我们需要公开他是无能力者\N{\fs12}Either way, we need to have him declared incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 无能力者吗  - 对\N{\fs12}- Incompetent? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,雷切尔需要控制他的股票来完成交易\N{\fs12}Rachel needs to control his stock to close the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,无能力者的想法相当有损人格  尼克\N{\fs12}An incompetency motion is pretty demeaning, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那  她想卖掉公司\N{\fs12}Well, she wants to sell the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对  但你不觉得有点过分了吗\N{\fs12}Yeah, but don't you think it's pushing a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我完全是个热心派的代表\N{\fs12}I mean, I'm all for zealous representation--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经提出动议了  我昨天就提了\N{\fs12}I've already filed the motion. I filed it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  你不觉得在我花了12个小时在读股东协议\N{\fs12}You know, don't you think it would've been a good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那些细则和公司的规章制度之前\N{\fs12}to tell me what you were doing before I spend 12 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你在干什么\N{\fs12}reading the the stockholders agreement, the bylaws
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好主意吗\N{\fs12}and the articles of incorporation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我们是在这儿一起工作的\N{\fs12}I thought we were working together here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是\N{\fs12}We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要一些海盗队的票吗\N{\fs12}Do you want some Pirates' tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不  谢谢\N{\fs12}No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我只有和史蒂夫在一起的美好经历\N{\fs12}Well, I haven't had anything but good experiences with Steve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他很聪明  工作努力  很擅长和客户打交道\N{\fs12}He's smart. He's hard working. He's very good with clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意  我认为他是个有价值的人\N{\fs12}I agree. I think he's a valuable addition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那么  所有赞成任命史蒂夫·格拉德查克为合伙人的\N{\fs12}Okay. So all in favor of nominating Steve Gladchuck for partner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,举起你们的右手\N{\fs12}raise your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  下一个候选人是桑德拉·凯斯尔\N{\fs12}Okay. Next candidate is Sandra Kestle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我  呃  我喜欢她  我觉得她不错\N{\fs12}l, uh...l like her. I think she's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克呢\N{\fs12}Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我也喜欢她  她聪明  坚强\N{\fs12}Yeah, I like her, too. She's smart. She's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我和她合作得很密切  在她开始和尼克工作之前\N{\fs12}I worked with her pretty closely until she started working with Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但  我觉得她很棒\N{\fs12}But I think she's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我没成功\N{\fs12}I didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很接近了  呃  它没完成\N{\fs12}It was close but, uh, it didn't get done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没完成\N{\fs12}Didn't get done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,委员会只是觉得你还没有完全准备好\N{\fs12}The committee just feels like you're not quite ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是委员会还是尼克\N{\fs12}The committee or Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,桑德拉  大家对你评价都很高\N{\fs12}Sandra, people think very highly of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是说评价高就能成为合伙人\N{\fs12}But not highly enough to make partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还不行  今年不行\N{\fs12}Not yet. Not not this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克说什么了\N{\fs12}What did Nick say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  我不能细说\N{\fs12}Oh, I can't go into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他否决了  是吗\N{\fs12}He was negative, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说吧  呃\N{\fs12}Let me just say that, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的意见都非常  非常有利\N{\fs12}the consensus was very, very favorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有利吗\N{\fs12}Favorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  呃  我们今晚什么也不用做\N{\fs12}Listen, uh, we don't have to do anything tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不  我想\N{\fs12}No. No, I'd like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那很好\N{\fs12}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 桑德拉太惨了  - 对\N{\fs12}- Too bad about Sandra. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个好律师\N{\fs12}She's a good lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但说实话  我很惊讶你会把她拉下来\N{\fs12}But to be honest, I was surprised you shot her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我发了你一份修改过的资产购买协议\N{\fs12}I sent you a copy of the revised asset purchase agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,收到了\N{\fs12}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,巴特勒签了字  这很好\N{\fs12}Butler signed off on it, so that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们需要尽快起草结案文件了\N{\fs12}So we need to start drafting up the closing documents pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他有问你为什么吗\N{\fs12}He asked you for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是说这些事\N{\fs12}He just says these things that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很害怕  如果他这么对他们的话\N{\fs12}They're scary... if he means them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是见鬼  我不是精神病医生\N{\fs12}But hell, I'm no psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有哪个孩子告诉我他想上吊的话  我会相信的\N{\fs12}lf some kid tells me he wants to hang himself, I believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在西南精神病院的医生觉得他只是想引起别的的注意\N{\fs12}The psychiatrist at Southwestern thinks he's just looking for attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那  我觉得我们应该把他送回去  今天\N{\fs12}Well, part of me thinks we should just send him back there... today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  为什么要搞这种事\N{\fs12}I mean, why screw around with this kinda thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们做错了什么  他会死的\N{\fs12}lf we're wrong about him, he'll be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们就会像两个白痴\N{\fs12}And we'll look like a couple of morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我正试着让你离开这儿\N{\fs12}I'm trying to get you outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是玩笑  德鲁\N{\fs12}It's not a joke, Drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能再说关于你自杀的事了\N{\fs12}You can't keep talking about killing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不行\N{\fs12}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因为大家是认真对待你的  即使你不明白\N{\fs12}Because people take you seriously, even if you don't mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我明白  - 你明白吗\N{\fs12}- I mean it. - You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白了吗  现在呢\N{\fs12}You mean it? Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经快要帮你找到一个很好的寄养家庭了\N{\fs12}We're this close to getting you a very good foster home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你必须停止说自杀的事了\N{\fs12}But you have to stop talking about suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不愿意  你就要回到西南精神病院去\N{\fs12}lf you don't, you will end up back in Southwestern.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一天关20个小时\N{\fs12}Lockdown 20 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这里不是真正的天堂\N{\fs12}This place isn't exactly paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我打电话给卡尔德的律师了\N{\fs12}I put in a call to Kalder's lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我已经告诉他了\N{\fs12}Yeah, I already talked to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说不能延长报价时间\N{\fs12}Said there's no way they'll extend the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好  - 那无能力者的议案可以实施了\N{\fs12}- Okay. - So the incompetency motion's at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克 我还是觉得如果我们遵守买卖协议的条款\N{\fs12}Nick, I still think if we followed the terms of the buy-sell agreement--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果委托人想卖  才是最有效的方法\N{\fs12}lf the client wants to sell, this is the most emective way to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢\N{\fs12}Great. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我不是你的员工  我是合伙人\N{\fs12}You know, I'm not your associate. I'm a partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,生意比你做的多  我要说的是\N{\fs12}with more business than you, and what I am saying is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的  真的不喜欢别人来告诉我该怎么做\N{\fs12}I'm really, really not so great about being told what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在\N{\fs12}- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  我只是  呃  我只是想告诉你那个\N{\fs12}Dad, I just, uh... I just wanted to tell you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我的投票  我的意见与你和桑德拉之间的关系无关\N{\fs12}my vote, my opinions had nothing to do with your relationship with Sandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能明白这点\N{\fs12}I hope you understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得她是个一般的律师\N{\fs12}I just think she's an average lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你不同意她在过去的三年里\N{\fs12}So you disagree with the excellent evaluation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,得到的优秀评价吗\N{\fs12}that she received over the last three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们觉得她很优秀  那就同意\N{\fs12}lf they characterize her as excellent, then yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,总体评价从1分到5比4\N{\fs12}Overall rating on a scale of one to five: four.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,评价说  桑德拉是一名出色的律师\N{\fs12}Comments: ''Sandra is an excellent lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,继续前进的步伐  她是个有价值的人才\N{\fs12}Continues to make great strides. She's a valued asset.''
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我知道这是我写的  那是  呃  两年前写的了\N{\fs12}Yeah, I know what I wrote. That was, uh... That was two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她昨晚辞职了\N{\fs12}she quit last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说得通\N{\fs12}Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  等等\N{\fs12}Wait a minute. Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫说得通\N{\fs12}What the helI's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  爸  我的意思是  她开始和执行合伙人约会\N{\fs12}Come on, Dad. I mean, she starts dating the managing partner
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就在合伙人投票前几周\N{\fs12}a few weeks before the partner vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她没被选上  然后就退出了\N{\fs12}She gets passed over and then she quits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她的做法很聪明\N{\fs12}It's very clear what she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  你错了\N{\fs12}Nicholas, you are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那她为什么辞职\N{\fs12}Then why did she quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定我能不能做得到\N{\fs12}I'm not sure I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不想它\N{\fs12}I just don't think it's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他真的明白发生了什么\N{\fs12}What if he really does understand what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他不想卖掉公司呢\N{\fs12}and he doesn't want to sell the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那  有别的选择  我们可以买下他的股票\N{\fs12}Right. Well, there are other choices, and we can buy out his stock--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经谈过了  杰克\N{\fs12}We've already talked about that, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那要花3个月的时间  卡尔德的报价会被扔进垃圾桶\N{\fs12}It'll take three months, and Kalder's offer would be in the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,雷切尔  我们说的是1500万美元\N{\fs12}Rachel, we're talking about $15 million here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是感觉不对\N{\fs12}It just feels wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的选择\N{\fs12}It's your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们应该这么做吗\N{\fs12}You think we should do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想卖掉公司  你应该这么做\N{\fs12}lf you want to sell the company, you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  如果查理有能力的话\N{\fs12}Listen, if Charlie were competent,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为他会拒绝这样的报价吗\N{\fs12}do you think that he would turn down an offer like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不会\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  你有答案了\N{\fs12}Well, there's your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,法官阁下  根据他的妻子和护理人员提供的证词\N{\fs12}Your Honor, based on testimony presented by his wife and caregivers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显  格赛特先生已经没有能力\N{\fs12}it is clear that Mr. Gossett is no longer capable
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,去评估与他财产有关的重要信息了\N{\fs12}of evaluating crucial information pertaining to his estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他是病人  法官阁下  很严重的病\N{\fs12}He is sick, Your Honor. Very sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他在交流方面有困难  但他是清醒的  他的思想是有意识的\N{\fs12}He has a dimicult time communicating. But he is aware, and his mind is alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,格赛特先生知道有一份报价  法官阁下\N{\fs12}Mr. Gossett knows there is an offer on the table, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他简单地选择了说  不\N{\fs12}He is simply choosing to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,欧文先生希望查理·格赛特是头脑清醒的\N{\fs12}Mr. Irving wants Charlie Gossett to be lucid,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这样他就能说服自己他是清醒的\N{\fs12}so much so that he's convincing himself that he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  我对枫树也可以做同样的事\N{\fs12}I mean, we could do the same thing with a maple tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你看着它足够久的话  它就会移动\N{\fs12}You stare at it long enough, it will move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟敢\N{\fs12}How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾  法官阁下  很遗憾\N{\fs12}It is sad, Your Honor. It is sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是格赛特先生在身体和精神上都不在场\N{\fs12}But Mr. Gossett is not mentally or physically present,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这样他不应该被允许管理他的财务状况\N{\fs12}and he should not be allowed to manage his financial affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  如果我们想的话我们可以接受那份报价卖掉公司\N{\fs12}So, we can accept the offer and sell the company if we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对  没错\N{\fs12}Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,像你说的  我们已经没有别的选择了  是吧\N{\fs12}Like you said, we really didn't have any other choice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我会安排一个和卡尔德的会议商量剩下的细节\N{\fs12}I'll set up a meeting with Kalder to go over the remaining details.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是觉得这是个糟糕的决定\N{\fs12}I still think it was a bad call.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们赢了  - 对\N{\fs12}- We won. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把自己和事务所  都放到了尴尬的境地\N{\fs12}We embarrassed ourselves and the firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嗨  伯顿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hi, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好吗  - 挺好的\N{\fs12}- How you doing? - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿了吗\N{\fs12}Are you hungry at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  我饿坏了\N{\fs12}I'm starving, as a matter of fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,来个三明治吧\N{\fs12}How about a sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好  进来吧  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- Yeah, come on in. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那  桑德拉  我有个主意\N{\fs12}So, Sandra, I got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不  呃  回来工作呢\N{\fs12}Why don't you, uh, come back to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿\N{\fs12}Burton...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白你为什么心烦  我真的明白\N{\fs12}I understand why you're upset. I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不能相信 我们不能想到可以\N{\fs12}But I can't believe we can't think of something
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,解决这些事情的方法\N{\fs12}that makes some sense to work this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  你已经离成为合伙人那么接近了\N{\fs12}You know, you were so close to making partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我不想看到你丢下这些离开\N{\fs12}Well, I hate to see you throw that all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,明年  顺便说一下  我认为你会成功的\N{\fs12}Next year, by the way, I think that you're gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感激  但是\N{\fs12}I appreciate that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我觉得我做了一个正确的决定\N{\fs12}No, I think I've made the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:22:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真的  我感觉相当好\N{\fs12}Truth is, I feel pretty good about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那  你已经有别的安排了吗\N{\fs12}Well, you have something lined up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有\N{\fs12}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想  你知道我很乐意帮你排忧解难\N{\fs12}lf you want, you know I'd be happy to help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这个镇上还是认识一些人的\N{\fs12}I still know a few people in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让你知道的\N{\fs12}I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那我问你\N{\fs12}Well, let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的关系对你的决定有任何影响吗\N{\fs12}Did our relationship influence your decision at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我辞职的决定和我们的关系没有任何关系\N{\fs12}My decision to resign had nothing to do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我来说很重要\N{\fs12}That's important for me to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿尔文  你有拉布隆特的文件吗  - 尼克  进来吧\N{\fs12}- Alvin, do you have the LaBonte file? - Nick, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  我只是在找那份文件\N{\fs12}No, I'm just looking for that file.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天早上在那个ALS的网站上\N{\fs12}I was on that ALS site this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.11,0:22:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,和一个家伙聊天  奥哈拉\N{\fs12}I was talking to a guy, O'Hara.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.64,0:22:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然后  奥哈拉今天早上起来  他的手臂发麻\N{\fs12}So, O'Hara wakes up this morning, and his arm is tingling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是躺在床上  想喝杯咖啡  他的手臂就发麻了\N{\fs12}He's just lying there in bed, about to have a cup of comee, and his arm's tingling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.48,0:22:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他说这是他感觉最可怕的事情\N{\fs12}Said it was the most frightening thing he ever felt
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:22:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是第一个迹象  一个开始\N{\fs12}because it was the first sign, the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.89,0:23:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.59,0:23:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在这些留言板上  很多人都在谈论自杀\N{\fs12}On these message boards, a lot of people talk about suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.34,0:23:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,互相给对方提示  建议\N{\fs12}Give each other tips, suggestions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.41,0:23:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,奥哈拉说这是条很好的界限  因为如果你做的太早\N{\fs12}O'Hara says it's a fine line, because if you do it too soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能会错过剩下的最后一点快乐\N{\fs12}you may miss out on the last little slice of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你等得太久  你就会失去完成的机会\N{\fs12}But if you wait too long, you lose the ability to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,爬上椅子  跳出窗外\N{\fs12}Climb up on a chair. Out a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你有拉布隆特的文件吗\N{\fs12}Do you have the LaBonte file?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,去露露的办公室试试\N{\fs12}Try Lulu's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  弗兰克·汤姆林森  汤姆林森塑料厂的\N{\fs12}Hi. Frank Tomlison. Tomlison Plastics.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 您有预约吗  - 有  来见伯顿·法林\N{\fs12}- Do you have an appointment here? - Yes, to see Burton Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.39,0:24:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我的秘书  琼  上周做了预约\N{\fs12}My secretary Joan made it last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.28,0:24:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,您好  我是伯顿·法林\N{\fs12}Hello, I'm Burton Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.08,0:24:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你被传唤了\N{\fs12}You've been served.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.76,0:24:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  桑德拉刚刚给我们发了传票和诉状\N{\fs12}Well, Sandra just hit us with a summons and complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.09,0:24:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她声称受到了性别歧视\N{\fs12}She's claiming sexual discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.49,0:24:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,歧视\N{\fs12}Discrimination?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.03,0:24:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,主要在于你和她之间的关系\N{\fs12}Primarily based upon your relationship with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.54,0:24:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  你在说什么\N{\fs12}What? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.84,0:24:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下诉状\N{\fs12}Read the complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.19,0:24:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一些指控说了你对待她的方式非常非常\N{\fs12}Some of the allegations she makes about the way you treated her
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.90,0:24:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,令人困扰  尼古拉斯\N{\fs12}are very, very disturbing, Nicholas.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.66,0:25:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.26,0:25:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你带了午餐过来  那我就带晚餐来了\N{\fs12}Since you brought over lunch, I figured I'd take care of dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.65,0:25:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\fs12}Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.53,0:25:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿\N{\fs12}Burton...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.12,0:25:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天来的时候我就想和你说关于诉讼的事\N{\fs12}when you came over today I wanted to tell you about the suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.28,0:25:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.98,0:25:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我说不出口  我太不安了\N{\fs12}But I couldn't. I was too nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.34,0:25:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,走到像你这样的人面前我说不出  抱歉\N{\fs12}It's not that easy to walk up to a guy like you and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.09,0:25:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你的儿子是个傲慢自大的混蛋  这样的话\N{\fs12}''Excuse me, but your son is an arrogant jerk.''
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.43,0:25:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  他是你儿子\N{\fs12}I mean, he's your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.82,0:25:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对  他是我儿子\N{\fs12}Yeah, he is my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.66,0:25:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他  他是个好男人\N{\fs12}And he's a... he's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.96,0:25:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好律师\N{\fs12}He's a good lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.85,0:25:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他很难搞  我知道\N{\fs12}He's tough, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.53,0:25:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但他不会性别歧视\N{\fs12}But he's not a sexist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.77,0:25:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那他为什么不投票给我\N{\fs12}Then why didn't he vote for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.10,0:25:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那你在发诉讼之前为什么没有告诉我呢\N{\fs12}Why didn't you tell me what was going on before you filed that suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.72,0:25:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要在我离开后做这些\N{\fs12}Why did you go behind my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.02,0:26:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 伯顿  - 我本来可以搞定一切的\N{\fs12}- Burton-- - I could've fixed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.74,0:26:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经气愤了很久了\N{\fs12}I've been so angry for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.32,0:26:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,当我没被选上的时候  我只是\N{\fs12}When I got passed over, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.35,0:26:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,打给我的律师  我说  去做吧\N{\fs12}I called my lawyer. I said, ''Let's do it.''
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.25,0:26:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.79,0:26:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有个办法能让大家都赢\N{\fs12}There is a way out so everybody wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.32,0:26:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你是让我撤回诉讼吗\N{\fs12}Are you asking me to drop the suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.85,0:26:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.47,0:26:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能这么做\N{\fs12}I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.54,0:26:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该走了\N{\fs12}I should probably go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.07,0:26:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我想  那是对的\N{\fs12}Yeah, I guess that... that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.47,0:27:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  我们需要谈谈\N{\fs12}Hi. We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.30,0:27:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得这是个好主意\N{\fs12}I don't think that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.93,0:27:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为我还是因为我爸\N{\fs12}ls this about me or my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.18,0:27:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你\N{\fs12}It's about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.90,0:27:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那和执行合伙人约会看来只是个小巧合了\N{\fs12}Well, it seems a little coincidental that you'd be dating the managing partner--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.20,0:27:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 太可笑了  我们是朋友  - 朋友吗\N{\fs12}- That's ridiculous. We're friends. - Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.35,0:27:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么阴谋  尼克\N{\fs12}There's no conspiracy here, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.07,0:27:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你父亲的陪伴  只是这样  没有其他的\N{\fs12}I enjoy your father's company, that's all. There's no agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.01,0:27:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这次的诉讼和他没有任何关系  是因为你\N{\fs12}This lawsuit has nothing to do with him. It has to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.66,0:27:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs12}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.23,0:27:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是我从法学院把你招进来的\N{\fs12}I'm the one that hired you out of law school.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.73,0:28:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一个36岁的一级助理  我给过你机会了\N{\fs12}A 36-year-old first year associate. I gave you your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.55,0:28:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你很可笑\N{\fs12}You're ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.83,0:28:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我可笑\N{\fs12}I'm ridiculous?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.69,0:28:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  如果我是你最大的困扰\N{\fs12}You know, if I'm your biggest problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.35,0:28:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那你只要回来和杰克工作就好了\N{\fs12}then just come back to the firm and work with Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.85,0:28:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不  谢谢\N{\fs12}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.68,0:28:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你再联系我的话  我会向州律师协会提出投诉\N{\fs12}lf you contact me again, I'll file a complaint with the State Bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.24,0:28:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿  尼克\N{\fs12}Hey, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.98,0:28:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你在做什么鬼事情\N{\fs12}What the hell do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.96,0:28:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,去桑德拉的家里找她吗\N{\fs12}Going over to Sandra's house like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.90,0:28:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我只是\N{\fs12}Well, I was just--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.47,0:28:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我在试着和她进行合理的谈话\N{\fs12}I was trying to have a rational conversation with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.68,0:28:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没起作用\N{\fs12}It didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.73,0:28:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那  你在期待什么\N{\fs12}Well, what'd you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.83,0:28:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你看过诉状了吗\N{\fs12}Did you read the complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.11,0:28:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看了  看了\N{\fs12}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.68,0:28:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,上面写的是真的吗\N{\fs12}ls it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.49,0:29:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,尼古拉斯  你有没有对她做过她说的那些事\N{\fs12}Nicholas, did you do the things she alleges you did or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.20,0:29:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  如果我做了  那也不是故意的\N{\fs12}Well, if I did, it wasn't intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.67,0:29:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,儿子  你要回答我  有还是没有\N{\fs12}Son, you gotta answer me yes or no,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.30,0:29:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我不知道\N{\fs12}l--l don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.99,0:29:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能说了一些我不该说的话  但是\N{\fs12}I might've said some things that I shouldn't have but...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.09,0:29:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是因为她是个女人\N{\fs12}it's not because she's a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.44,0:29:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  所以你就对待别人像对待垃圾一样  你是这个意思吗\N{\fs12}Oh, so you just treat everybody like crap. Is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.75,0:29:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.22,0:29:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该去伴侣心理辅导\N{\fs12}I think we should go to couples counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.28,0:29:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.72,0:29:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  很明显  呃  我对一些事还是非常不安\N{\fs12}I mean, I'm obviously, uh, still very upset about certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.18,0:29:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.36,0:29:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想心里辅导可能会有帮助\N{\fs12}So I think it might help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.09,0:29:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我  我不知道\N{\fs12}Yeah. l--l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.27,0:30:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我希望我们可能可以  呃\N{\fs12}You know, I'd hoped that we could maybe, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.70,0:30:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,先一起解决问题\N{\fs12}work things out together first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.14,0:30:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对  但是那个策略并没有很成功\N{\fs12}Yeah, but that strategy hasn't been very successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.66,0:30:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不太擅长应付治疗\N{\fs12}I'm just not very good with therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.49,0:30:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  但是如果我们能坐下和某个人\N{\fs12}I know, but maybe if we go and sit down with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.95,0:30:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谈谈这个问题  也许会有帮助的\N{\fs12}and talk about this stuff, it will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.10,0:30:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对  但  我有段不愉快的经历  呃\N{\fs12}Right. Well, I have a hard time, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.01,0:30:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下来和我不认识的人聊天\N{\fs12}sitting down talking to a person that I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.44,0:30:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我还要付钱\N{\fs12}and that I'm paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.17,0:30:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.29,0:30:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜和德鲁·扬科夫斯基的寄养家庭吵架了\N{\fs12}The foster family that Suzanne was talking to for Drew Jankowski fell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.38,0:30:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很紧张关于自杀的事\N{\fs12}They were nervous about the suicide thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.97,0:30:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那个我提到的家庭  他们改变主意了\N{\fs12}That family that I mentioned, they changed their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.58,0:30:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fs12}Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.33,0:30:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的觉得我可以做到\N{\fs12}I really think I might do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.12,0:30:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,只要尽快完成\N{\fs12}Just get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.23,0:30:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fs12}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.83,0:31:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么  - 跟我来就行了\N{\fs12}- Why? - Just come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.50,0:31:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,放下耳机\N{\fs12}Leave that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.42,0:31:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把耳机放下\N{\fs12}Just leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.46,0:31:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你就待在这儿\N{\fs12}You just wait here.
