Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.65,0:31:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  我有两张海盗的票  位置很好\N{\fs12}Look, I have two Pirates' tickets, great seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.88,0:31:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要我帮你去看海盗队的球赛吗吗\N{\fs12}You need my help to go to a Pirates' game?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.32,0:31:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我需要你帮助一个委托人\N{\fs12}No, I need your help with a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.24,0:31:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那个孩子\N{\fs12}The kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.84,0:31:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 自杀的那个吗  - 对  德鲁\N{\fs12}- The suicidal one? - Yeah. Drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.60,0:31:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,露露不想我接这个案子\N{\fs12}Lulu doesn't want me to take that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.01,0:31:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我想\N{\fs12}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.58,0:31:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要给卡尔德一份过去三年所有审计过的财务报表\N{\fs12}We need to get Kalder a copy of all the audited finances for the last three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.91,0:31:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs12}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.96,0:32:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,以及未解决诉讼的摘要\N{\fs12}And a summary of outstanding litigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.97,0:32:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  做完了\N{\fs12}Uh, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.44,0:32:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs12}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.42,0:32:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你有  呃\N{\fs12}Have you, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.96,0:32:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你有看过桑德拉的诉讼吗\N{\fs12}Have you read Sandra's complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.26,0:32:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,看了\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.25,0:32:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有一些相当严重的指控\N{\fs12}Some pretty serious allegations in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.39,0:32:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,雷切尔·格赛特刚才打电话来了\N{\fs12}Rachel Gossett just called.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.53,0:32:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她不能来开这个会了\N{\fs12}She's not gonna be able to make the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.14,0:32:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她的丈夫去世了  几小时前\N{\fs12}Her husband died a few hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.06,0:32:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs12}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.72,0:32:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.98,0:32:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.20,0:32:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\fs12}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.72,0:32:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他的死不是我们的错\N{\fs12}It's not our fault he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.83,0:32:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是\N{\fs12}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.16,0:32:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.65,0:32:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我希望玩得开心  就算海盗队输掉了\N{\fs12}Well, I hope you had a good time, even though the Pirates lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.22,0:32:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  差点儿赢了\N{\fs12}Yeah. It was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.24,0:33:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,10比1吗\N{\fs12}10-1?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.09,0:33:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,德鲁\N{\fs12}Drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.82,0:33:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所有我们今晚聊的这些  你的妈妈  那些孩子\N{\fs12}Everything we talked about tonight, your mom, those kids--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.68,0:33:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.90,0:33:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很痛苦\N{\fs12}It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.08,0:33:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,太痛苦了\N{\fs12}It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.36,0:33:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,人可以是卑鄙的\N{\fs12}People can be mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.04,0:33:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.90,0:33:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,人也会死亡\N{\fs12}And people die.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.98,0:33:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这很难过\N{\fs12}And it's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.89,0:33:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想  我可以接受你的案子\N{\fs12}lf you want, I can take over your case,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.48,0:33:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你找到合适寄养家庭\N{\fs12}help you find the right foster home.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.43,0:33:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那个叫尼克的怎么办\N{\fs12}What about that Nick guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.80,0:33:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他会理解的\N{\fs12}He'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.29,0:33:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.58,0:33:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在这期间\N{\fs12}ln the meantime,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.18,0:33:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你在想伤害你自己的事情时  能先打电话给我的话  我会很高兴的\N{\fs12}if you're thinking about hurting yourself, I'd appreciate it if you'd call me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.21,0:33:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.62,0:33:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.16,0:33:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见\N{\fs12}See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.14,0:34:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在吗\N{\fs12}- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.52,0:34:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有时间吗\N{\fs12}You have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.92,0:34:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.22,0:34:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个艰难的谈话\N{\fs12}This is a difficult conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.98,0:34:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果可以的话  我就直说了\N{\fs12}so I intend to speak candidly, if that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.77,0:34:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么\N{\fs12}What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.30,0:34:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们几个今天吃午餐的时候在讨论桑德拉的诉讼\N{\fs12}A few of us had lunch today to discuss Sandra's lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.11,0:34:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们几个\N{\fs12}A few of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.38,0:34:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  执行委员会  除了你和尼克\N{\fs12}Well, the executive committee, minus you and Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.91,0:34:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们决定聘请外部律师\N{\fs12}We've decided to retain outside counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.44,0:34:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不让我做顾问吗\N{\fs12}Without consulting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.59,0:34:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到指控说的  伯顿\N{\fs12}Considering the allegations, Burton,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.67,0:34:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们觉得最好别把你牵扯进来\N{\fs12}we figured it was better to leave you out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.81,0:35:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经聘请了贝丝·雅各布森  她是一名劳工律师\N{\fs12}We've hired Beth Jacobson. She's a labor attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.95,0:35:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她的名气很大\N{\fs12}She's got a great reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.74,0:35:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她想在早上和尼克见面\N{\fs12}She wants to interview Nick in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.94,0:35:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,总之  我只是想在我们采取行动之前让你知道\N{\fs12}Anyway, I just wanted to let you know before we made a move on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.68,0:35:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来像是你已经开始行动了  杰克\N{\fs12}Sounds like you're already moving on it, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.02,0:35:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,桑德拉主张说你曾经让她帮你在一家叫Lucque的饭店\N{\fs12}Sandra claims that you once asked her to make a reservation for you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.14,0:35:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,预订过房间\N{\fs12}at a restaurant called Lucque's.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.31,0:35:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  对  我是  呃\N{\fs12}Uh, yeah, I was, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.87,0:35:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我开会迟到了\N{\fs12}I was running late into a meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.07,0:35:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我记得我答应过把客户带到那儿\N{\fs12}and I remembered that I promised to take a client there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.91,0:35:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,接着就  我让她帮我预定了  这没什么\N{\fs12}And yeah, I asked her to make a reservation. No big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.02,0:35:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你让她打了电话吗\N{\fs12}So you asked her to call?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.10,0:35:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.63,0:36:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前有让男同事打电话去预约吗\N{\fs12}Did you ever ask a male associate to call and make a reservation?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.60,0:36:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  呃\N{\fs12}Uh... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.56,0:36:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  不记得了\N{\fs12}I don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.94,0:36:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  我不知道\N{\fs12}Uh... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.41,0:36:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么是从来不回电话或者邮件\N{\fs12}What is this never returning phone calls or e-mails thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.56,0:36:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以是真的喽\N{\fs12}So it's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.45,0:36:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  有时候我工作的时候  我喜欢自己做事情\N{\fs12}You know, sometimes when I'm working, I like to do things myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.75,0:36:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你不回复在你手底下工作的人的电话或者邮件吗\N{\fs12}You don't return calls or e-mails from people who work under you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.99,0:36:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你有过不回男同事的电话十次吗\N{\fs12}Have you ever not returned 10 calls from a male associate?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.69,0:36:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  够了  我  我不知道\N{\fs12}Oh, come on. l--l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.42,0:36:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法把这些事都记录下来\N{\fs12}I don't keep a record of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.14,0:36:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,四个月前你有把桑德拉踢出客户会议吗\N{\fs12}Did you kick Sandra out of a client meeting about four months ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.94,0:36:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我  我让她离开了\N{\fs12}Yeah, l--l asked her to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.61,0:36:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在一个重要的男性执行总裁客户的面前吗\N{\fs12}ln front of a male CEO of an important client?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.86,0:36:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她  她拖延了会议的进度\N{\fs12}She was--she was slowing down the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.23,0:37:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她问了很多无意义的问题  而我试着把注意力集中在这个工作上\N{\fs12}She was asking pointless questions, and I was trying to focus on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.94,0:37:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我要求她离开了\N{\fs12}And yes, I asked her to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.63,0:37:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉她  滚出去\N{\fs12}You told her to ''Get out.''
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.16,0:37:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我是让她离开\N{\fs12}I asked her to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.56,0:37:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次表示我的哀悼  葬礼办得很好\N{\fs12}Again, my condolences. It was a beautiful service.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.81,0:37:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.44,0:37:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以坐下来谈一谈\N{\fs12}We are going to have to sit down and talk--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.57,0:37:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.50,0:38:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,公正的合伙人进行了投票\N{\fs12}The disinterested partners took a vote,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.12,0:38:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们决定尽快与桑德拉达成和解\N{\fs12}and we've decided to settle with Sandra as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.71,0:38:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.59,0:38:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,跟她闹上法庭我们没好处  理由很明显\N{\fs12}There's no upside to litigating this with her, for obvious reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.03,0:38:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我同意这个说法\N{\fs12}Well, I don't disagree with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.34,0:38:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还安排了2点的会议讨论尼克的情况\N{\fs12}We've also scheduled a meeting for 2:00 to discuss Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.93,0:38:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,讨论尼克什么\N{\fs12}Discuss Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.53,0:38:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他的态度  他的保证\N{\fs12}His attitude. His commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.51,0:38:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,还有他的时间\N{\fs12}And his hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.92,0:38:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他做兼职赚了很多钱  伯顿\N{\fs12}He gets paid a lot of money to work part-time, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.93,0:38:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在是在告诉你试着在争取足够的投票来开除我儿子吗\N{\fs12}Are you telling me you're trying to round up enough votes to fire my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.66,0:38:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.81,0:38:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在告诉你我们安排了2点的会议讨论关于尼克的事\N{\fs12}I'm telling you that we've scheduled a meeting for 2:00 to discuss Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.97,0:39:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,葬礼的事怎么样了\N{\fs12}How was the funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.83,0:39:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我和情感顾问约好了明天下午见面\N{\fs12}I made an appointment with a couples counselor for tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.98,0:39:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.59,0:39:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  好像人们  呃\N{\fs12}Uh, it seems people, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.99,0:39:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我眼中的自己和别人不一样  我觉得\N{\fs12}I see myself differently than others do, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.76,0:39:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,总之  如果你觉得太晚的话\N{\fs12}Anyway, if you don't think it's too late then--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.89,0:39:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  没有太晚\N{\fs12}No, it's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.52,0:39:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.46,0:39:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候我向你求婚的时候你为什么说  不\N{\fs12}Why did you say no when I asked you to marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.01,0:40:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.08,0:40:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们可以在我们咨询的时候谈\N{\fs12}Maybe we can talk about that when we...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.57,0:40:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢  对  - 好\N{\fs12}- Oh, yeah. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.83,0:40:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  顺便说一句\N{\fs12}Oh, and by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.97,0:40:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到那条裙子了\N{\fs12}I saw the dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.12,0:40:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴是个女孩\N{\fs12}I'm glad it's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.86,0:40:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我就期待是女孩\N{\fs12}I was rooting for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.62,0:40:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼克  - 阿尔文\N{\fs12}- Nick. - Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.11,0:40:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我为德鲁找了一个很棒的寄养家庭\N{\fs12}I found this great foster family for Drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.35,0:40:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs12}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.76,0:40:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  如果你不介意  我想接手他的案子\N{\fs12}So, if you don't mind, I'd like to take over his case.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.03,0:40:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可以  但是不要告诉露露\N{\fs12}Yeah. But just don't tell Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.22,0:40:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿  - 嘿\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.63,0:40:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有时间吗  - 有\N{\fs12}- You got a second? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.71,0:40:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我想为发生在桑德拉身上的事道歉\N{\fs12}Listen, I wanted to apologize for what happened with Sandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.19,0:40:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我希望我没有搞砸你和她之间的事\N{\fs12}You know, I hope I didn't screw things up for you and her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.84,0:41:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  我们问了那个律师  贝丝  会尽快和解这个诉讼  所以\N{\fs12}No. We asked that lawyer, Beth, to settle it as quickly as possible, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.71,0:41:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果你觉得那是最好的  - 是的\N{\fs12}- If you think that's best. - I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.81,0:41:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.32,0:41:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有个执行委员会的会议\N{\fs12}It's an executive committee meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.62,0:41:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没有叫我\N{\fs12}They didn't call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.51,0:41:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你没被邀请\N{\fs12}You weren't invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.56,0:41:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要开除我吗\N{\fs12}They gonna fire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.13,0:41:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在讨论这个\N{\fs12}They're talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.25,0:41:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有选票了吗\N{\fs12}They have the votes?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.14,0:41:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克觉得有了\N{\fs12}Jake thinks so.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.03,0:41:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意见可能还有些用\N{\fs12}My opinion might still mean something.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.66,0:41:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你要投哪一票\N{\fs12}Which way are you gonna vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.30,0:41:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  别闹了\N{\fs12}Well-- Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.46,0:41:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我是认真的\N{\fs12}No, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.64,0:41:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,儿子  你是个非常好的律师\N{\fs12}Son, you're a very good lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.46,0:41:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,对  如果我不是你的儿子  你会投哪一票\N{\fs12}Yeah, if I weren't your son, which way would you vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.54,0:41:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但你是我的儿子  而且你是个了不起的律师\N{\fs12}But you are my son, and you're a hell of a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.74,0:41:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你还没有回答我的问题  爸\N{\fs12}Well, you're not answering my question, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.12,0:41:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我在想什么吗\N{\fs12}You know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.59,0:41:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为你应该做对事务所最有利的事\N{\fs12}I think you should do what's best for the firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.96,0:41:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  我觉得你应该做对事务所最有利的决定\N{\fs12}I mean it. I think you should do what is best for the firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.61,0:41:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs12}Right.
